.@KGeorgieva: Women are disproportionately affected by #COVID19 because they are:
1- more likely to work in service sectors;
2- employed in the informal sector; &amp;
3- bear the burden of more household work
#IMFmeetings #inclusiverecovery #GenderEquality https://t.co/0jZJ5bBEcL

1) An early public health response is key to flattening the virus curve;
2) Easing containment measures only after the virus is subdued seems to bring about better economic outcomes;
3) Fiscal support is critical to reduce economic costs and underpin the recovery.
